#: buildVars.py:15
msgid "freeRadio"
msgstr "自由广播"

#: buildVars.py:19
msgid ""
"FreeRadio is an internet radio add-on for NVDA that provides seamless access to thousands of stations via the Radio Browser open directory. It features a fully accessible station browser with search, country filter, favourites management, and per-station audio profiles. Playback is "
"handled by a prioritised backend chain (BASS, VLC, PotPlayer, Windows Media Player) with support for volume control, audio effects, output device selection, and simultaneous audio mirroring to a second device. Additional features include instant and scheduled recording, sleep and alarm "
"timers, automatic ICY metadata announcements, Shazam-based music recognition, and a liked-songs log. All controls and shortcuts are designed for NVDA accessibility."
msgstr ""
"自由广播是一个适用于 NVDA 的互联网广播附加组件，通过 Radio Browser 开放目录提供对数千个电台的无缝访问。它具有一个完全可访问的电台浏览器，支持搜索、国家/地区筛选、收藏管理和每个电台的音频配置文件。播放由优先化的后端链（BASS、VLC、PotPlayer、Windows Media Player）处理，支持音量控制、音频"
"特效、输出设备选择和同时将音频镜像到第二个设备。其他功能包括即时和计划录音、睡眠和闹钟定时器、自动 ICY 元数据播报、基于 Shazam 的音乐识别以及收藏歌曲日志。所有控件和快捷键均专为 NVDA 无障碍访问而设计。"

#: buildVars.py:26
msgid ""
"\n"
"**New features**\n"
"- Favourites can now be exported to JSON or M3U format and imported back from either format. Export and Import buttons appear at the bottom of the Favourites tab. When importing, you can choose to merge the file's stations into your existing list or replace the list entirely. Duplicate "
"stations (matched by ID or stream URL) are skipped automatically during merge.\n"
"- The Recordings and Timer tabs now have a Filter field above their favourite station lists, matching the one already present in the Favourites tab. The Liked Songs tab also has a Filter field above the song list. In all cases, pressing the Down arrow from the filter field moves focus "
"directly into the list, and the number of matching results is announced after each keystroke.\n"
"**Added a Lyrics Service**\n"
"Asynchronous lyrics fetcher for the Liked Songs tab using the lrclib.net API (free, no API key required).\n"
"- Fetches lyrics in the background via a daemon thread; the UI remains responsive during lookup.\n"
"- Prefers `plainLyrics`; falls back to `syncedLyrics` with LRC timestamps stripped when plain text is unavailable. Tracks marked as instrumental are silently skipped.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"**新功能**\n"
"- 收藏现在可以导出为 JSON 或 M3U 格式，并可从任一格式导入回系统。导出和导入按钮出现在“收藏”选项卡的底部。导入时，您可以选择将文件中的电台合并到现有列表中，或完全替换列表。合并期间会自动跳过重复的电台（通过 ID 或流媒体 URL 匹配）。\n"
"- “录音”和“计时器”选项卡现在在收藏电台列表上方增加了筛选字段，与“收藏”选项卡中已有的字段一致。“收藏歌曲”选项卡也在歌曲列表上方增加了筛选字段。在所有情况下，从筛选字段按向下箭头键会将焦点直接移入列表，并且每次击键后都会播报匹配的结果数量。\n"
"**增加了歌词服务**\n"
"使用 lrclib.net API (免费，无需 API 密钥) 为“收藏歌曲”选项卡提供的异步歌词获取器。\n"
"- 通过守护线程在后台获取歌词；UI 在查找期间保持响应。\n"
